  * Implement option --devunversioned. Closes: bug#530368.
  * Implement option --ignorelibdep. Closes: bug#530367.
  * Support control file fields spanning multiple lines. Closes:
    bug#573396.
  * Maintained using Git: Add Vcs-* stanzas.
  * Repackage using CDBS. Build-depend on cdbs.
  * Set debhelper compat level to 6. Build-depend tightened to that
    version.
  * Stop depending on debianutils or apt: essential and required version
    of debianutils satisfied in oldstable.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 3.8.4.
  * Rewrite copyright file to draft DEP5 rev. 135.

